@NODE Bugs "Bugs"

The Dimensions values of jpeg Files may not shown accurate.

(Thats not from my Programm)
The jpeg.libary(WOS Version) dont like it if its accessed from 2 Tasks at the same time, it does
display errors then or crash the whole computer. Its known from PhotoFolio already. Similar
happends with WarpDTs. My Programm works around that, the Tasks works syncron. Its not much
slower cause of them just x seconds with 2260 pictures against loading them 2 times allone.
That means of course too its not allowed to use other programms, while loading, that decodes
pictures too over the jpeg.library or the WarpDTs at the same time.


@ENDNODE
